Then in Anaconda Promt --- give  --- conda create -n myenv python=3.7
Once the new environment is created give --- activate myenv
And the give cd and path of your folder
Once you inside the Working Directory -- Launch jupyter notebook


After coding everthing go to a new anaconda promt terminal 
There give activate myenv
There give -- pip freeze --all > requirements.txt
